# Usage:
#   Copy this file to deploy.conf and update with your Pi's actual values:
#     cp deploy/deploy.conf.example deploy/deploy.conf
#
#   deploy.conf is gitignored and will not be committed.
#
# Sourced by deploy/deploy-pi.sh (Pi tier).
# Variables here override the script defaults; unset variables fall through to
# the defaults baked into the script.
# ==============================================================================

# Raspberry Pi 5 (chi-eclipse-01) connection details
